IPLD is the data model of the content-addressable web. It allows us to treat all hash-linked data structures as subsets of a unified information space, unifying all data models that link data with hashes as instances of IPLD. IPLD是内容可寻址网络的数据模型。它允许我们将所有的哈希链接的数据结构视为一个统一的信息空间的子集，将所有用哈希链接的数据模型统一为IPLD的实例。

Why IPLD? 为什么是IPLD？

A data model for interoperable protocols. 一个可互操作协议的数据模型。

Content addressing through hashes has become a widely-used means of connecting data in distributed systems, from the blockchains that run your favorite cryptocurrencies, to the commits that back your code, to the web’s content at large. Yet, whilst all of these tools rely on some common primitives, their specific underlying data structures are not interoperable. 通过哈希值进行内容寻址已经成为分布式系统中连接数据的一种广泛使用的手段，从运行你喜欢的加密货币的区块链，到支持你的代码的提交，再到整个网络的内容。然而，尽管所有这些工具都依赖于一些共同的基元，但它们特定的底层数据结构是不可互操作的。

Enter IPLD: IPLD is a single namespace for all hash-inspired protocols. Through IPLD, links can be traversed across protocols, allowing you to explore data regardless of the underlying protocol. 进入IPLD：IPLD是一个单一的命名空间，用于所有哈希启发的协议。通过IPLD，可以跨越协议的链接，使你可以探索数据，而不考虑底层协议。

Use cases 应用案例

The sky’s the limit as IPLD allows you to work across protocol boundaries. The point is that IPLD provides libraries that make the underlying data interoperable across tools and across protocols by default. 天空是无限的，因为IPLD允许你跨越协议边界工作。重点是，IPLD提供的库使底层数据在默认情况下可以跨工具和跨协议互操作。

Bitcoin to Git比特币到Git

Reference your latest commits in a git branch to a bitcoin transaction to timestamp your work. By linking your git commit, you can view the commit from your blockchain explorer. 将你在git分支中的最新提交内容引用到比特币交易中，为你的工作盖上时间戳。通过链接你的git提交，你可以从你的区块链资源管理器查看提交。

Ethereum to IPFS以太坊到IPFS

Have your next contract refer to media on IPFS, perhaps modifying it and tracking its changes on each function execution. Seamlessly jump from function to object through IPLD addressing. 让你的下一个合约参考IPFS上的媒体，也许是修改它，并在每次函数执行时跟踪其变化。通过IPLD寻址，无缝地从函数跳转到对象。

Features 特质

A canonical data model 一个规范的数据模型

A self-contained descriptive model that uniquely identifies any hash-based data structure and ensures the same logical object always maps to the exact same sequence of bits. 一个独立的描述性模型，可以唯一地识别任何基于哈希的数据结构，并确保同一逻辑对象总是映射到完全相同的比特序列。

Protocol independent resolution 独立于协议的解决方案

IPLD brings isolated systems together, making integration with existing protocols simple. IPLD将孤立的系统聚集在一起，使与现有协议的整合变得简单。

Upgradeable 可升级

With Multiformats support, IPLD is easily upgradeable and will grow with your favorite protocols. 由于支持Multiformats，IPLD很容易升级，并将与您最喜爱的协议一起成长。

Operates across formats 可跨格式操作

Express your IPLD objects in various serializable formats like JSON, CBOR, YAML, XML and many more, making IPLD a cinch to use with any framework. 用各种可序列化的格式表达你的IPLD对象，如JSON、CBOR、YAML、XML等，使IPLD在任何框架下都能轻松使用。

Backwards compatible 向后兼容

Non-intrusive resolvers make IPLD easy to integrate within your existing work. 非侵入性的解析器使IPLD很容易集成到你现有的工作中。

A namespace for all protocols 一个适用于所有协议的命名空间

IPLD allows you to explore data across protocols seamlessly, binding hash-based data structures together through a common namespace. IPLD允许你无缝地探索跨协议的数据，通过一个共同的命名空间将基于哈希的数据结构绑定在一起。

Media媒体

IPLD is an open source project from the IPFS community. There are many ways you can contribute by getting involved. Learn more about IPLD from the community. IPLD是IPFS社区的一个开源项目。你可以通过多种方式参与其中，做出贡献。从社区中了解更多关于IPLD的信息。
